snippet: New England Patriots coach Bill Belichick lamented the missed big plays in a 20-18 loss to the Denver Broncos on Sunday but it was a little one that ultimately may have cost the defending champions a return trip to the Super Bowl....
lead_paragraph: New England Patriots coach Bill Belichick lamented the missed big plays in a 20-18 loss to the Denver Broncos on Sunday but it was a little one that ultimately may have cost the defending champions a return trip to the Super Bowl.

headline.main: Little Mistake Ends Patriots Super Bowl Defense
headline.print_headline: Little Mistake Ends Patriots Super Bowl Defense
